      • Config

        public Config(java.lang.String name,
              javax.sql.DataSource dataSource,
              Dialect dialect,
              java.lang.Boolean showSql,
              java.lang.Boolean devMode,
              java.lang.Integer transactionLevel,
              IContainerFactory containerFactory,
              ICache cache)
        Constructor with full parameters
        パラメータ:
        dataSource - the dataSource, can not be null
        dialect - the dialect, set null with default value: new MysqlDialect()
        showSql - the showSql,set null with default value: false
        devMode - the devMode, set null with default value: false
        transactionLevel - the transaction level, set null with default value: Connection.TRANSACTION_READ_COMMITTED
        containerFactory - the containerFactory, set null with default value: new IContainerFactory(){......}
        cache - the cache, set null with default value: new EhCache()
